Since the author is allowing this free version of his book to be distributed via torrent, please take the time to do a favor for him.

Go to the Amazon page (http://www.amazon.com/PSYCHO-SUCCESS-ebook/dp/B00CB3NQDC) and leave a review and/or buy the $4 eBook.
Just what we need: A manual for bastards to become really accomplished.
